{"id": 3084, "genre": 1001, "title": "身为一个当代人，你觉得哪些生活技能是一定要掌握的？", "description": "尤其是那些“虽然没有写在课本里，但是你却发现意外好用”的当代技能。（题图来自：视觉中国 ©️ Jane_Kelly）", "record_count": 2078, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191208230753eC54DPOIxVfE8Kzj.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-12-08T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 350210, "content": "即便独处时也不要过于放纵自己 保持精致+自律", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673901}, {"id": 350211, "content": "学会免疫各种骚扰", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451145}, {"id": 350213, "content": "学会独处。有自己的兴趣爱好。\n（以前大家都说你要巴拉巴拉，长大后很多时候是自己决定巴拉巴拉……", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553407}, {"id": 350725, "content": "能独立做完一生中可能会做的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434374}, {"id": 350214, "content": "1.做饭\n2.早睡\n3.独立思考\n4.拒绝的能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1494457}, {"id": 350215, "content": "留出给自己思考甚至发呆的空闲时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673971}, {"id": 350216, "content": "《新闻编辑室》里的那句『相信理性、知识和远见，而不是庸众的狂欢』", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194233}, {"id": 350217, "content": "控制自己的欲望", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1627500}, {"id": 350220, "content": "保持诱惑，独立思考。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181244}, {"id": 350222, "content": "学会相信自己，控制情绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673993}, {"id": 350223, "content": "be real", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644283}, {"id": 350224, "content": "阅读原文（外语）的能力吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957686}, {"id": 352528, "content": "立足现实 兼顾理想", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1445390}, {"id": 350225, "content": "迅速整理情绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631549}, {"id": 350226, "content": "怎样为人父母？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1591352}, {"id": 352276, "content": "1.独立和知识变现的能力  \r\n2.可以奋不顾身的真诚  \r\n3.讨人喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1679438}, {"id": 350229, "content": "分清楚fact 和opinion", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318584}, {"id": 350232, "content": "寻找信息源头然后自我判断的能力。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1491277}, {"id": 350233, "content": "。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1637828}, {"id": 350234, "content": "现代人出现的所有问题，古代都出现过。变得是环境，不变的，是人心。没事多翻翻历史。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674014}, {"id": 350235, "content": "学会独处", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667730}, {"id": 350236, "content": "你刚说什么，我没听到😄", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227146}, {"id": 350237, "content": "知道自己对别人是不重要的 摆好定位", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117612}, {"id": 350238, "content": "平常心", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674021}, {"id": 350239, "content": "忘记", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1607507}, {"id": 350240, "content": "逛淘宝的时候不要总觉得下一个看见的商品更好，要买就买果断下手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1045750}, {"id": 350241, "content": "博学明辨慎思笃行", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1617711}, {"id": 350244, "content": "当局者迷，旁观者清～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1406861}, {"id": 350253, "content": "在繁杂的世界中找寻自己心动之人（物）", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205349}, {"id": 350254, "content": "筛选信息", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588249}, {"id": 350255, "content": "过滤无用信息", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674062}, {"id": 350258, "content": "克制 自律 慎独", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1586457}, {"id": 350259, "content": "能够见人说鬼话！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284224}, {"id": 350266, "content": "PPT\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674135}, {"id": 350267, "content": "自我愉悦", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1091442}, {"id": 350268, "content": "无论在什么群体里，自己都要有自己的想法，随大流不一定对，也不一定好。", "image": "img/option/option/20191210205737qfdJl12GDmWI7po6", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674151}, {"id": 350270, "content": "学会习惯朋友的去留\n懂得天底下哪有不散的宴席", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1478843}, {"id": 350271, "content": "自生的强大\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674170}, {"id": 350273, "content": "独立，独自生存", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673893}, {"id": 350274, "content": "自我愉悦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1339020}, {"id": 350285, "content": "从网络获取信息并鉴别哪些有效", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1544523}, {"id": 350541, "content": "察颜观色", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274335}, {"id": 352333, "content": "自信勇敢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680555}, {"id": 350542, "content": "独立思考，理性分析，客观描述。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373892}, {"id": 350292, "content": "学会开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613919}, {"id": 350293, "content": "理性思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674256}, {"id": 350294, "content": "知道自己的目标，清楚自己的位置", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1453902}, {"id": 350296, "content": "视觉and大脑屏蔽网络与现实垃圾信息", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674092}, {"id": 350298, "content": "在信息潮涌中学会自我思考和判断，在快节奏的生活里学会慢下来看书、思考、散步，在部分自由泛滥的方面（性爱、熬夜、网络言论、娱乐等）学会自我管理", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1566748}, {"id": 350299, "content": "知止", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1566748}]}